PN,41801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774102277
OL,3,CMassive 500-metre long fatberg
OL,4,Cdiscovered clogging sewers outside
OL,5,CHeathrow
OL,7,FA massive fatberg big enough to
OL,8,Fstretch between two airport terminals
OL,9,Fhas been discovered beneath the roads
OL,10,Foutside Heathrow's Terminal 5.
OL,12,FThe 500-metre long fatberg found by
OL,13,FThames Water engineers, was clogging a
OL,14,Fsewer near the airport and is the
OL,15,Fequivalent of more than 700 suitcases
OL,16,Flaid end to end.
OL,18,FIt was discovered beneath Poyle Road,
OL,19,Fan area dominated by industrial units
OL,20,Fand airport perimeter businesses.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774102277
OL,3,CMassive 500-metre long fatberg
OL,4,Cdiscovered clogging sewers outside
OL,5,CHeathrow
OL,7,FEngineers say as the section of sewer
OL,8,Fstays full for long periods, fat
OL,9,Fdeposits build up quickly, causing
OL,10,Frepeated blockages.
OL,12,FRemoving it took over two weeks, with
OL,13,Fengineers using excavation tools to
OL,14,Fchip away at the solid mass before
OL,15,Fblasting the remaining deposits with
OL,16,Fhigh-pressure water jets.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774102277
OL,3,CMassive 500-metre long fatberg
OL,4,Cdiscovered clogging sewers outside
OL,5,CHeathrow
OL,7,FThames Water says across its network,
OL,8,Ffats, oils and grease cause more than
OL,9,F20,000 blockages every year,
OL,10,Faccounting for 28% of all sewer
OL,11,Fblockages, and they lead to over 60%
OL,12,Fof sewer floods and cost around #40
OL,13,Fmillion annually.
OL,15,FA recent survey found more than 40% of
OL,16,Fpeople had poured meat juices down the
OL,17,Fsink, 39% gravy, 18% animal fats
OL,18,Fincluding lard, 28% cream, 21% custard
OL,19,Fand 10.5% hummus ` all fatty and oily
OL,20,Fsubstances that can congeal in pipes
OL,21,Fand block them up.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774102277
OL,3,CMassive 500-metre long fatberg
OL,4,Cdiscovered clogging sewers outside
OL,5,CHeathrow
OL,7,FThey can wreak havoc on drainage
OL,8,Fsystems and, in the worst cases, lead
OL,9,Fto homes and gardens being flooded
OL,10,Fwith sewage and pollution in our
OL,11,Frivers.
OL,13,FAll of these substances can congeal in
OL,14,Fpipes, causing blockages that lead to
OL,15,Fsewer flooding, polluted waterways
OL,16,Fand, in the worst cases, sewage
OL,17,Fbacking up into homes and gardens.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774102277
OL,3,CMassive 500-metre long fatberg
OL,4,Cdiscovered clogging sewers outside
OL,5,CHeathrow
OL,7,FSteve Crabb, Head of Waste Operations
OL,8,Ffor Thames Water home counties, said:
OL,9,F"This was a stubborn and sizeable
OL,10,Fblockage, but our teams have worked
OL,11,Frelentlessly to break it down and keep
OL,12,Fthe network flowing.
OL,14,F"Fatbergs like this are entirely
OL,15,Favoidable, and we're urging everyone
OL,16,Fincluding businesses to think
OL,17,Fcarefully about what they pour down
OL,18,Fthe drain to help us prevent repeats
OL,19,Fof this in future."
OL,26,@qD@AOU{D@SO]
